The paper discusses a neural network accelerator architecture using ReRAM technology, which falls under the category of emerging technologies (cs.ET). The paper also focuses on the design and optimization of the hardware and software system stack, which falls under the categories of architecture (cs.AR), neural networks (cs.NE), and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of spiking schema and memory blocks, which could be related to the category of embedded systems (cs.EM).
